snippet.textDisplay:
PLEASE TAKE ONE SECOND TO READ THIS.

There is a lot of hate and cruelty and evil going around in the world, and its really hard to witness things like this. The acts of some people are scary and terrifying and sometimes you forget that people like this even exist. I am not one of those people. I always try to help whenever i possibly can, to help put atleast one good thing in the world. I know im not the only one. You are too. You probably feel as disgusted as i do when you hear things like this happen. We can put something good in this world.

My school, Stony Brook University, is hosting a trip to help people in Dominican Republic. However, the fees are too expensive for me, a broke college student, to be able to pay for. We can make a difference collectively, but I will need your help to help do just that. Please, anything will go a long way. Thank you so much!
